							Late Fall 2016	
							.fa.fa-users{style:"color:#aa4b41;"} |
							6-9 travelers
						.upcoming-description
							With local guides and a fleet of ultra-portable packrafts, trek along remote logging roads, follow animal trails, and paddle unnamed tributaries through the upper Amazon...
						%a{href: "/peru"}
							.upcoming-trip-btn.btn
								Claim this Trip

		.col-md-6.upcoming-trip-block
			.upcoming-trip
				.upcoming-img{style: "background: url('#{asset_path("background/TrestlesBeachhomepage.jpeg")}') center center no-repeat; background-size: cover;"}
