							Exploring southern California's ocean, desert and mountains all in one weekend. Go from rock climbing and camping in Joshua Tree National Park, to surfing the waves of Malibu...
						%a{href: "/socaltrifecta"}
							.upcoming-trip-btn.btn
								Claim this Trip

